# Manifest contract:
# - legacy format: name|url|branch|dest_dir
# - extended format: name|url|branch|dest_dir|pinned_commit_sha
#   - pinned_commit_sha is optional, but when set, verify_external_sources.sh
#     enforces remote branch contains that commit and sync-clone checks it out.
